metadata.title: Bathymetry of the Anadyr Gulf, Russia

creators.name: U.S. Geological Survey (USGS), Alaska Biological Science Center, Marine

metadata.description: Bathymetric contours of the Anadyr Gulf and Bering Strait in Russian waters at 1:1,000,000 scale. Digitized from the "Bathymetry Map of the Bering Shelf" (Geological Society of America, 1974).
metadata.notes:
Purpose: This coverage was created to support marine mammal and bird research at the USGS Alaska Biological Science Center.
